  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The study aimed to compare CT-based virtual autopsy with classic autopsy as a tool for
      quality control in intensive care medicine.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      The study aimed to compare CT-based virtual autopsy with classic autopsy as a tool for
      quality control in intensive care medicine. Especially with respect to complications during
      intervention like catheter pacement.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
